      <p>Nh&#7857;m m&#7909;c &#273;&iacute;ch k&#7871; ti&#7871;p truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng hi&#7871;u h&#7885;c, u&#7889;ng n&#432;&#7899;c nh&#7899; ngu&#7891;n, l&aacute; l&agrave;nh &#273;&ugrave;m l&aacute; r&aacute;ch c&#7911;a m&#7843;nh &#273;&#7845;t Th&#7915;a Thi&ecirc;n-Hu&#7871; th&acirc;n y&ecirc;u, c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i con n&#7863;ng t&igrave;nh v&#7899;i qu&ecirc; h&#432;&#417;ng v&agrave; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i y&ecirc;u Hu&#7871;, &#273;ang sinh s&#7889;ng t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam v&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i, ti&#7871;n h&agrave;nh v&#7853;n &#273;&#7897;ng x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng Qu&#7929; Gi&aacute;o D&#7909;c Hu&#7871; Hi&#7871;u H&#7885;c (vi&#7871;t t&#7855;t QGD HHH) nh&#7857;m g&oacute;p ph&#7847;n nh&#7887; v&agrave;o s&#7921; nghi&#7879;p gi&aacute;o d&#7909;c &#7903; qu&ecirc; nh&agrave;.</p>
      <p>Qu&#7929; Gi&aacute;o D&#7909;c Hu&#7871; Hi&#7871;u H&#7885;c b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u h&#7885;at &#273;&#7897;ng t&#7915; th&aacute;ng 8 n&#259;m 2005 t&#7853;p h&#7907;p th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n, x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng &#273;&#7873; &aacute;n, gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u, &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; t&ecirc;n mi&#7873;n, thi&#7871;t k&#7871; website, tranh th&#7911; c&aacute;c s&#7921; &#7911;ng h&#7897; ban &#273;&#7847;u.</p>
      <p>Qu&#7929; &#273;&atilde; ra m&#7855;t v&agrave; trao h&#7885;c b&#7893;ng t&#7841;i Tp HCM ng&agrave;y 08-01-2006; Th&agrave;nh Ph&#7889; Hu&#7871; ng&agrave;y 22-01-2006.</p>
      <p>Qu&#7929; GD HHH &#273;&atilde; c&oacute; <a href="http://www.huehieuhoc.com/index.php?fod=tch&act=qd2384"><strong>Quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh ch&iacute;nh th&#7913;c</strong></a> th&agrave;nh l&#7853;p v&agrave;o ng&agrave;y 13 th&aacute;ng 10 n&#259;m 2006 l&agrave; m&#7897;t t&#7893; ch&#7913;c phi ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; (NGO), phi l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n, c&oacute; con d&#7845;u v&agrave; t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n ri&ecirc;ng t&#7841;i ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng nh&#432; sau:  </p>
      <p><strong>T&ecirc;n &#273;&#417;n v&#7883;:</strong> QU&#7928; GI&Aacute;O D&#7908;C HU&#7870; HI&#7870;U H&#7884;C</p>
      <p><strong>S&#7889; t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n: </strong></p>
      <p><strong>- VN&#272;:</strong> 22415479</p>
      <p><strong>-  USD:</strong> 22415509</p>
      <p>        Ng&acirc;n H&agrave;ng C&#7893; Ph&#7847;n Th&#432;&#417;ng M&#7841;i &Aacute; Ch&acirc;u (ACB)</p>
      <p>&nbsp;</p>
      <p><strong>N&#7897;i dung h&#7885;at &#273;&#7897;ng ch&iacute;nh:</strong></p>
      <p>        <strong>1. </strong>Ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh h&#7885;c b&#7893;ng, khen th&#432;&#7903;ng cho c&aacute;c em h&#7885;c sinh sinh vi&ecirc;n ngh&egrave;o, hi&#7871;u h&#7885;c.</p>
      <p>        <strong>2.</strong> Ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh h&#7893; tr&#7907; trang thi&#7871;t b&#7883;, x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng tr&#432;&#7901;ng l&#7899;p.</p>
      <p><strong> 3.</strong> Ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh V&#259;n Th&#7875; M&#7929; &#273;&#7875; gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c em ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n to&agrave;n di&#7879;n.</p>
      <p>Qua h&#417;n m&#7897;t n&#259;m ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, Qu&#7929; Gi&aacute;o D&#7909;c Hu&#7871; Hi&#7871;u H&#7885;c &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; &#7911;ng h&#7897; nhi&#7879;t t&igrave;nh c&#7911;a nhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p, h&#7897;i &#273;o&agrave;n, gia &#273;&igrave;nh, c&aacute; nh&acirc;n trong v&agrave; ngo&agrave;i n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7875; trao t&#7863;ng nhi&#7873;u h&#7885;c b&#7893;ng cho c&aacute;c em gia c&#7843;nh kh&oacute; kh&#259;n, hi&#7871;u h&#7885;c - v&#7853;n &#273;&#7897;ng kinh ph&iacute; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng tr&#432;&#7901;ng ti&#7875;u h&#7885;c - trao nhi&#7873;u hi&#7879;n v&#7853;t gi&aacute; tr&#7883; (m&aacute;y vi t&iacute;nh, &aacute;o qu&#7847;n&hellip;) c&#361;ng nh&#432; tham gia c&#7913;u tr&#7907; b&atilde;o l&#7909;t.</p>
      <p>        Qu&#7929; Gi&aacute;o d&#7909;c Hu&#7871; Hi&#7871;u H&#7885;c &#273;&atilde; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7841;ng l&#432;&#7899;i th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n, H&#7897;i &#272;&#7891;ng C&#7889; V&#7845;n, H&#7897;i &#272;&#7891;ng Qu&#7843;n L&yacute; v&agrave; Ban Gi&aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c &#272;i&#7873;u H&agrave;nh t&#7915;ng b&#432;&#7899;c ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&agrave; l&#7899;n m&#7841;nh, l&agrave;m c&#7847;u n&#7889;i gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c nh&agrave; h&#7843;o t&acirc;m v&#7899;i h&#7885;c sinh sinh vi&ecirc;n, c&#361;ng nh&#432; ng&agrave;nh gi&aacute;o d&#7909;c t&#7841;i qu&ecirc; nh&agrave;.</p>
      <p>Qu&#7929; Gi&aacute;o D&#7909;c Hu&#7871; Hi&#7871;u H&#7885;c ch&acirc;n th&agrave;nh c&#7843;m &#417;n nh&#7919;ng &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p c&#7911;a c&aacute;c nh&agrave; h&#7843;o t&acirc;m trong th&#7901;i gian qua v&agrave;
        mong nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; &#7911;ng h&#7897; nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n v&#7873; t&agrave;i l&#7921;c, c&ocirc;ng s&#7913;c v&agrave; tr&iacute; tu&#7879; c&#7911;a Qu&yacute; V&#7883; &#273;&#7875; Qu&#7929; Gi&aacute;o D&#7909;c Hu&#7871; Hi&#7871;u H&#7885;c ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng l&#7899;n m&#7841;nh, g&oacute;p ph&#7847;n n&agrave;o v&agrave;o s&#7921; nghi&#7879;p gi&aacute;o d&#7909;c c&#7911;a qu&ecirc; h&#432;&#417;ng Th&#7915;a Thi&ecirc;n-Hu&#7871; gi&agrave;u truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng hi&#7871;u h&#7885;c v&agrave; nh&acirc;n &aacute;i.        <br>
